sequenceDiagram
    participant Provider as Provider System<br/>(HIS/EMR)
    participant PS as Provider Service<br/>provider-service
    participant SDK as HCX SDK<br/>integration-sdks
    participant AG as API Gateway<br/>hfcx-platform
    participant BL as Business Logic<br/>hfcx-platform
    participant REG as Registry<br/>sunbird-rc-core
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL
    participant KAFKA as Message Queue<br/>Kafka
    participant PayerSDK as Payer SDK<br/>integration-sdks
    participant Payer as Payer System

    Note over Provider,Payer: 1. Eligibility Check Workflow
    Provider->>PS: Check patient eligibility
    PS->>SDK: Create eligibility request
    SDK->>REG: Lookup payer public key
    REG-->>SDK: Return public key
    SDK->>SDK: Encrypt payload (JWE)
    SDK->>AG: POST /coverageeligibility/check
    AG->>AG: Authenticate & validate
    AG->>BL: Route to eligibility service
    BL->>DB: Store request
    BL->>KAFKA: Publish eligibility event
    BL-->>AG: Return request ID
    AG-->>SDK: 202 Accepted
    SDK-->>PS: Request submitted
    PS-->>Provider: Eligibility check initiated

    KAFKA->>BL: Process eligibility event
    BL->>REG: Lookup payer endpoint
    REG-->>BL: Return payer details
    BL->>PayerSDK: Forward encrypted request
    PayerSDK->>Payer: Deliver eligibility check
    Payer->>Payer: Decrypt & process
    Payer-->>PayerSDK: Eligibility response
    PayerSDK->>AG: POST /coverageeligibility/on_check
    AG->>BL: Process response
    BL->>DB: Store response
    BL->>KAFKA: Publish response event
    BL-->>AG: Acknowledge
    AG-->>PayerSDK: 200 OK

    KAFKA->>BL: Process response event
    BL->>SDK: Notify provider
    SDK->>PS: Eligibility response
    PS->>Provider: Display coverage details

    Note over Provider,Payer: 2. Pre-Authorization Workflow
    Provider->>PS: Submit pre-auth request
    PS->>SDK: Create pre-auth request (FHIR)
    SDK->>REG: Lookup payer public key
    REG-->>SDK: Return public key
    SDK->>SDK: Encrypt payload
    SDK->>AG: POST /preauth/submit
    AG->>BL: Route to pre-auth service
    BL->>DB: Store request
    BL->>KAFKA: Publish pre-auth event
    BL-->>AG: Return request ID
    AG-->>SDK: 202 Accepted

    KAFKA->>BL: Process pre-auth event
    BL->>PayerSDK: Forward to payer
    PayerSDK->>Payer: Deliver pre-auth request
    Payer->>Payer: Review & adjudicate
    Payer-->>PayerSDK: Approval/Denial
    PayerSDK->>AG: POST /preauth/on_submit
    AG->>BL: Process response
    BL->>DB: Update pre-auth status
    BL->>SDK: Notify provider
    SDK->>PS: Pre-auth response
    PS->>Provider: Display approval status

    Note over Provider,Payer: 3. Claim Submission Workflow
    Provider->>PS: Submit claim
    PS->>SDK: Create claim request (FHIR)
    SDK->>SDK: Attach pre-auth reference
    SDK->>SDK: Encrypt payload
    SDK->>AG: POST /claim/submit
    AG->>BL: Route to claims service
    BL->>DB: Store claim
    BL->>KAFKA: Publish claim event
    BL-->>AG: Return claim ID
    AG-->>SDK: 202 Accepted

    KAFKA->>BL: Process claim event
    BL->>PayerSDK: Forward to payer
    PayerSDK->>Payer: Deliver claim
    Payer->>Payer: Adjudicate claim
    Payer-->>PayerSDK: Claim response
    PayerSDK->>AG: POST /claim/on_submit
    AG->>BL: Process response
    BL->>DB: Update claim status
    BL->>SDK: Notify provider
    SDK->>PS: Claim adjudication result
    PS->>Provider: Display payment amount

    Note over Provider,Payer: 4. Payment Notification
    Payer->>PayerSDK: Payment processed
    PayerSDK->>AG: POST /paymentnotice/request
    AG->>BL: Process payment notice
    BL->>DB: Record payment
    BL->>SDK: Notify provider
    SDK->>PS: Payment received
    PS->>Provider: Update financial records
